title: What's for Dinner?  A Delightfully Disgusting Menu
description: The next time you ask your mom, "What's for dinner?" - watch out! You may end up with deep-fried eyeballs on your plate. When you read this book, be prepared to scrunch your nose, pop out your eyes, and scream, "EEEEWWWW!" You'll never ask that question again.
author: Paige Miller
